name: Interactive Book Collection # Hansel and Gretel
description:
This book is part of the Interactive Book Collection, published by justlows.

Since this NFT is interactive, it is possible to read the entire book! You can flip the pages by clicking and dragging or by using your arrow keys of the keyboard.


Hansel and Gretel is a fairy tale collected by the Brothers Grimm, about a brother and a sister abandoned in a forest, where they fall into the hands of a witch who lives in a house made of gingerbread, cake, and pastries.
